abstract_str: 60 % of estate agents believe owning a home is becoming less achievable . residential property prices jumped an average of 6.8 % in the last year . gen y couple katherine ross and __hauaru__ gilbert are struggling to buy . artemis __paniaras__ and fiancee william said they were n't taken seriously . both couples would like more property advice available to young people . sydney lord mayor said that many young people can not afford to buy .
